The '''StarWars.com Message Boards''', formerly located on [[StarWars.com]], were the official ''[[Star Wars]]'' online discussion forums. The message boards included separate boards for the movies, the [[Star Wars Legends|Expanded Universe]], boards accessible only to [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace fan club]] members and even a non&ndash;''[[Star Wars]]'' forum called the Cantina, where fans could talk about anything. The boards were primarily moderated by a team of volunteers. The boards opened on [[October 9]], [[2001]] and were closed on [[June 3]], [[2011]].

